  "detailed_description": "\"My life as a cat\" is a relaxing, slow-paced visual novel about longing for something different than the modern society and searching back to nature. It has AI-generated oil paintings to illustrate the fully voiced and texted story as you progress through it according to your choices.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWill you have what it takes to survive out in the wilderness, or will you steer towards a not-so-favorable ending?",
